      <data key="edge_doi">10.1199/tab.0103</data>
      <data key="edge_evidence">The GA20ox overexpression lines display early flowering and increased stem growth phenotypes, whereas GA2ox overexpression lines show late flowering and dwarf phenotypes</data>
